tags.description:
An easy 1.0-mile loop that wanders past numerous soccer fields and the universally accessible playground. 

It is a great neighborhood trail with easy access from the parking lot. 

Trail Length:
1.0 mile

Trail Type:
Shared-use

Trail Level:
Easy
